+* The default code style is changed from `intellij_idea` to `ktlint_official`. This code style adheres to the best parts of the Kotlin Coding Conventions and Android Kotlin style guide. It is no longer restricted to produce code compatible with the default IntelliJ IDEA formatter. Existing projects can retain the old behavior by setting `.editorconfig` property `ktlint_code_style` to `intellij_idea`.
